query:
SELECT
            sn.id
        FROM
            scheduled_notifications sn
        LEFT JOIN
            availability a ON sn.avail_id = a.id AND a.is_valid = TRUE
        LEFT JOIN
            usrs u ON a.usr_id = u.id AND u.is_valid = TRUE
        WHERE
            sn.is_valid = TRUE
            AND a.id IS NULL
            OR u.id IS NULL;
